{
  "stem": "2230.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] In the wall, there was a-- on every corner, there was a square block on the bottom cut out so that the water from the drains can go through and run out.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Well, being scrawny, little kids, as we were at that time, we would crawl out at night and run away.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Go to the villages where you came from.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Go to the fields.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Get a potato, a sugar beet, whatever you could.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Come back to the ghetto and feed your family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I had sisters and my mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was the man of the house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[CRYING] There was a streetcar about two blocks from where we lived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I just saw it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The only thing left of the streetcar lines is about 10 feet of it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The street car, that would come in from one end, go around of the Jewish ghetto, and go out to the other side.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Like, they didn't want to divert the travel line of the streetcar, so that they wouldn't go through the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we would jump on it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There were Polish police.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There were Ukraine police.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there were German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The Ukraines were worse than the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If they caught us, not only did they take everything away, they would beat the heck out of us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The Polacks, sometimes they would keep it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they would say, OK, what you got in your pockets?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you had a zloty, you gave it to him, everything was fine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
